---
title: Rogan Josh Pulled Beef Loaded Naans with Mustard Seed Potatoes, Pickled Onion and Mint Yoghurt
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, these tasty Rogan Josh Pulled Beef Loaded Naans are perfect for a casual sharing-style dinner.
